abstract: Cambridge United and Manchester United play out scoreless draw in forth round of FA Cup; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: The fourth-tier club Cambridge United held visiting Manchester United to a 0-0 draw in the fourth round of the F.A. Cup on Friday.
snippet: The fourth-tier club Cambridge United held visiting Manchester United to a 0-0 draw in the fourth round of the F.A. Cup on Friday.

headline.main: Manchester United Held to Tie in F.A. Cup
